text: I have two eyes so I can see and nose to smell.
I have ten fingers that can touch.
I have two ears so I can hear...
I have a tongue inside my mouth to taste the food I eat.
I have two eyes so I can see and nose to smell.
I have ten fingers that can touch, they do it very well.
I have two ears so I can hear the birds up in the trees.
I have a tongue inside my mouth to taste the food I eat.
